              </p>
            </div>

            <div
              class="sm:p-10 p-5 bg-gray-50 sm:me-5 mb-10 rounded-md hover:shadow-md"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl mb-5 font-bold">Web Development</h3>
              <p class="leading-10 text-gray-500 text-justify">
                As a seasoned web development professional, I offer
